## Gapminder

```{r gap_first, eval = FALSE,  width = 8, class = "offset-2", title = "global vs individual trend"}
library(gapminder)
gapminder %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = year, y = lifeExp, group = country)) +
  geom_line()
